Phoenix::

"I'm here," Phoenix states, reaching the control room.  Now 
Switchblade can see just why Flicker fell for her in the first place. 
 Nearly invisible before under her "battle scars", her red plating is 
accented by gold trim, which touches up her well-formed curves nicely. 
 She's not the most gorgeous femme around, but she's quite capable of 
turning heads; if she had the aptitude for it, she could be an 
excellent temptress.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Jeff" <x_rauq_x@y...> wrote:
> -- Switchblade --
> 
> "There's a small issue of me not trusting you alone in my--" 
> Switchblade pauses for a fraction of a second, then corrects 
> himself, "the Predacons ship... I've got to go pick up a supply 
> ship, and you're coming with me."
> 
> He taps the side of his infrared optic impatiently. "So, hurry up."
